      • getSubVisitor

        public QueryVisitor getSubVisitor(BooleanClause.Occur occur,
                                  Query parent)
        Pulls a visitor instance for visiting child clauses of a query The default implementation returns this, unless occur is equal to BooleanClause.Occur.MUST_NOT in which case it returns EMPTY_VISITOR
        Parameters:
        occur - the relationship between the parent and its children
        parent - the query visited
